{"text_id":189181,"tokens":["In"," the"," context"," of"," animal"," vision",","," having"," night"," vision"," and"," losing"," the"," ability"," to"," see"," color"," are"," not"," necessarily"," directly"," correlated","."," While"," it"," is"," true"," that"," many"," species"," that"," possess"," exceptional"," night"," vision",","," such"," as"," cats"," and"," owls",","," often"," have"," limited"," or"," absent"," color"," vision",","," this"," is"," not"," a"," universal"," characteristic","."," There"," are"," several"," examples"," of"," animals"," that"," can"," see"," in"," low"," light"," conditions"," without"," compromising"," their"," ability"," to"," perceive"," color","."," For"," instance",","," some"," species"," of"," fish",","," like"," the"," bar","bels"," and"," the"," cave","fish",","," have"," evolved"," to"," thrive"," in"," dark"," environments"," and"," simultaneously"," retain"," their"," ability"," to"," see"," vibrant"," colors","."," Similarly",","," some"," primates",","," such"," as"," the"," nocturnal"," bush","babies",","," possess"," night"," vision"," capabilities"," and"," still"," have"," a"," keen"," sense"," of"," color"," vision",".","\n\n","In"," the"," case"," of"," humans",","," it"," is"," indeed"," a"," common"," phenomenon"," to"," experience"," color"," vision"," limitations"," in"," low","-","light"," conditions","."," This"," is"," due"," to"," the"," way"," our"," ret","inas"," are"," structured"," and"," the"," amount"," of"," time"," it"," takes"," for"," the"," rods"," to"," adapt"," to"," darkness","."," However",","," this"," is"," not"," necessarily"," a"," direct"," result"," of"," night"," vision"," itself",","," but"," rather"," an"," interaction"," between"," the"," visual"," pathways"," involved"," in"," color"," perception"," and"," those"," responsible"," for"," low","-","light"," adaptation","."," It"," is"," essential"," to"," recognize"," that"," even"," in"," humans",","," color"," vision"," is"," not"," lost"," as"," a"," result"," of"," night"," vision",","," but"," rather"," becomes"," more"," challenged"," and"," less"," reliable"," in"," low","-","light"," conditions",".","\n\n","In"," conclusion",","," having"," night"," vision"," does"," not"," automatically"," or"," unavoid","ably"," mean"," losing"," the"," ability"," to"," see"," color","."," The"," relationship"," between"," these"," two"," visual"," capabilities"," is"," more"," complex"," and"," dependent"," on"," the"," unique"," adaptations"," of"," each"," species"," or"," individual","."," There"," are"," numerous"," examples"," of"," animals"," and"," even"," humans"," that"," can"," possess"," exceptional"," night"," vision"," while"," still"," retaining"," their"," ability"," to"," perceive"," color",","," albeit"," potentially"," with"," reduced"," accuracy"," in"," certain"," conditions","."],"sub_source":"reddit","model":"llama3-8b","label":1}